{"tid":262041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【失蹤29小時】Bosco證實當場不治   鑑證科人員到場","createTime":"2017-05-29T02:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T03:57:37.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb399f85794c9c5aefbdd947c4ab552d2a47223","tid":262041,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170529/large/1496014974_4076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170529%2Flarge%2F1496014974_4076.jpg&h=a5d8cbf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【10:09】警方證實Bosco當場不治<br />\n【09:50】事主仍未被救下山，但警方鑑證科人員到場<br />\n【08:50】消防員今晨8時24分在藍田廣田邨附近山邊找到事主，他昏迷不醒。<br />\n<br />\n穿迷彩衫褲20歲青年郭葦諾﹝Bosco﹞，在將軍澳靈實醫院對上山頭失蹤，失蹤29小時後被發現伏屍山頭，警方正封鎖現場展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方、消防及民安隊通宵搜索，至今早擴大範圍，兵分四路分頭搜索，其中兩隊由藍田公園登山，第1隊直上山頂配水庫，第2隊則走另一條較遠路線登上山頂，第3隊由將軍澳馬游塘上山，第4隊則由將軍澳澳景路維景灣畔上山。早上7時許，澳景路的隊伍已到達山頂，惟未有發現，稍後會到另一地點搜索。<br />\nBosco的胞兄Eric今早接受《蘋果》記者電話訪問，他坦言現階段不肯定是意外還是什麼，不過胞弟之前一直沒有異樣，出發前﹝周六晚﹞一家人吃晚飯，還計劃他行完夜山，周日早上飲早茶，「係有planning(計劃)嘅！」<br />\n而Bosco以往也會下午或夜晚出動行山打War game的習慣。同行的三名朋友，都是玩War game認識的，各人也有行山經驗，一般不會行叢林或抄小路。Eric續說，Bosco讀完VTC及相關課程後做冷氣技工學徒，至今9個月至1年。家中只他兩兄弟，父母都非常擔心。<br />\n<br />\nBosco失蹤時身穿迷彩衫褲、並戴上頭盔及電筒，不排除與朋友上山打War game。<br />\n消防員今晨8時24分在藍田廣田邨附近山邊找到事主，他昏迷不醒。據了解，由廣田邨出發至發現Bosco的位置，至少要行30分鐘的山路才能到達。不過，發現Bosco一個多小時後，他仍未被救下山，但警方鑑證科人員卻到場調查。至今早10時許，警方證實Bosco當場不治。"},{"pid":"ba4f5e670badf23d1609710be73e3d1b3175d456","tid":262041,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"成單野好撚鬼"},{"pid":"ec33ad4c1a700157c7b0b6fab5b29a0fbb6acfca","tid":262041,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1213b54247b190f623d4abf1c176234118234ee1","tid":262041,"uid":49285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"點會有人無啦啦4點幾打俾佢之後佢就落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee17181d3442a23f4a25cd5a82b6425a4b1d3049","tid":262041,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe59e3d70911d3b0cb73711f82de484cc10f43ea","tid":262041,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/114742_6166088a31feab03738d821917f89a46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F114742_6166088a31feab03738d821917f89a46.jpg&h=8c6bc6df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75c0d256a86be4b12ac978b72dec60d8130b567e","tid":262041,"uid":10296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13020deea2b9756f4c517df7422ca3346141107d","tid":262041,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:51:05.000Z","msg":"當場不治可能係割喉"},{"pid":"e1429b4bcc00ee70998a6971bf391045d28ebae2","tid":262041,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"真係謀殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c1d7e8ae0d6d5915bb363f316e28efa4e4eb45","tid":262041,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:57:37.000Z","msg":"2017年版三五成群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}